high_descs: Walk to the sink on the left side.
Pick up the bar of soap from the left side of the sink.
Turn around to face the back of the toilet.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and face the sink on the right side.
Pick up the bar of soap from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and face the back of the toilet.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet, to the right of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Walk forward and around the toilet to left bathroom sink
Pick up the soap bar from the sink
Turn around and walk up to the right side of the toilet
Put the soap bar on top of the back of the toilet
Turn around and walk up to the right bathroom sink
Pick up the soap bar from the sink
Turn around and walk back to the right side of the toilet
Put the soap bar on top of the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the soap bars on top of the toilet

high_descs: Walk around the toilet to the leftmost sink.
Pick up the soap from inside the sink.
Turn around and face the side of the toilet.
Place the bar of soap on the toilet tank, close to the front left corner.
Turn left and walk to the rightmost sink.
Pick up the soap from inside the sink.
Turn left and walk again to the closest side of the toilet.
Place the bar of soap on the toilet tank behind the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap on a toilet tank.
